Ed said:

 It appears my oil cooler has begun to leak.

 On a 1700 Type IV does the engine need to come out to change the seals?

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-

I honestly doubt your oil cooler is leaking.
99% of the time, the oil sender is leaking.
It is right above the oil cooler and runs down.
Replace the sender FIRST.
